==Hindi==
===Etymology===
From Sanskrit [[विना]]

===Postposition and preposition===
'''बिना'''
# [[without]], prepared without
#:बिना दूध चाय (binā dūdh chāy) - Tea without milk

===Usage===
बिना is one of the only times a preposition ever appears in Hindi.

